              "id": "ae745797",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "text-editor",
              "settings": {
                "editor": "<h2 data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"67\"><strong data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"67\">Commercial Polished Concrete: Durable, Sleek, and Built to Last</strong></h2><p data-start=\"69\" data-end=\"312\">Polished concrete is more than a flooring option. It\u2019s modern, durable, and low maintenance. Whether you\u2019re building new or refreshing existing floors, Midland Floor Care delivers polished concrete that looks sharp and performs under pressure.</p><p data-start=\"314\" data-end=\"357\"><strong data-start=\"314\" data-end=\"357\">Why businesses choose polished concrete</strong></p><ul data-start=\"358\" data-end=\"716\"><li data-start=\"358\" data-end=\"437\"><p data-start=\"360\" data-end=\"437\">Professional appearance: high-gloss or satin finishes that reflect your brand</p></li><li data-start=\"438\" data-end=\"513\"><p data-start=\"440\" data-end=\"513\">Extreme durability: stands up to heavy foot traffic and rolling equipment</p></li><li data-start=\"514\" data-end=\"583\"><p data-start=\"516\" data-end=\"583\">Low maintenance: easy to clean and more stain resistant when sealed</p></li><li data-start=\"584\" data-end=\"655\"><p data-start=\"586\" data-end=\"655\">Cost-effective lifecycle: outlasts many materials with minimal upkeep</p></li><li data-start=\"656\" data-end=\"716\"><p data-start=\"658\" data-end=\"716\">Sustainable option: uses the existing slab to reduce waste</p></li></ul><p data-start=\"718\" data-end=\"763\"><strong data-start=\"718\" data-end=\"763\">Our commercial polished concrete services</strong></p><ul data-start=\"764\" data-end=\"1129\"><li data-start=\"764\" data-end=\"839\"><p data-start=\"766\" data-end=\"839\">Surface preparation: grinding, patching, and cleaning for a flawless base</p></li><li data-start=\"840\" data-end=\"912\"><p data-start=\"842\" data-end=\"912\">Polishing and finishing: multiple grit levels from matte to high gloss</p></li><li data-start=\"913\" data-end=\"978\"><p data-start=\"915\" data-end=\"978\">Staining and color enhancement: rich tones and branding accents</p></li><li data-start=\"979\" data-end=\"1051\"><p data-start=\"981\" data-end=\"1051\">Protective sealing: added resistance to stains, moisture, and abrasion</p></li><li data-start=\"1052\" data-end=\"1129\"><p data-start=\"1054\" data-end=\"1129\">Ongoing maintenance programs: scheduled polishing to keep the finish strong</p></li></ul><p data-start=\"1131\" data-end=\"1154\"><strong data-start=\"1131\" data-end=\"1154\">Industries we serve</strong></p><ul data-start=\"1155\" data-end=\"1357\"><li data-start=\"1155\" data-end=\"1193\"><p data-start=\"1157\" data-end=\"1193\">Corporate offices and headquarters</p></li><li data-start=\"1194\" data-end=\"1225\"><p data-start=\"1196\" data-end=\"1225\">Retail stores and showrooms</p></li><li data-start=\"1226\" data-end=\"1259\"><p data-start=\"1228\" data-end=\"1259\">Hotels and hospitality venues</p></li><li data-start=\"1260\" data-end=\"1289\"><p data-start=\"1262\" data-end=\"1289\">Restaurants and breweries</p></li><li data-start=\"1290\" data-end=\"1318\"><p data-start=\"1292\" data-end=\"1318\">Educational institutions</p></li><li data-start=\"1319\" data-end=\"1357\"><p data-start=\"1321\" data-end=\"1357\">Warehouses and industrial facilities</p></li></ul><p data-start=\"1359\" data-end=\"1385\"><strong data-start=\"1359\" data-end=\"1385\">Why Midland Floor Care</strong></p><ul data-start=\"1386\" data-end=\"1649\"><li data-start=\"1386\" data-end=\"1459\"><p data-start=\"1388\" data-end=\"1459\">Specialized equipment: commercial grinders, polishers, and dust control</p></li><li data-start=\"1460\" data-end=\"1526\"><p data-start=\"1462\" data-end=\"1526\">Expert technicians: trained for the demands of commercial spaces</p></li><li data-start=\"1527\" data-end=\"1591\"><p data-start=\"1529\" data-end=\"1591\">Minimal downtime: flexible scheduling to keep business running</p></li><li data-start=\"1592\" data-end=\"1649\"><p data-start=\"1594\" data-end=\"1649\">Full-service partner: installation through ongoing care</p></li></ul><p data-start=\"1651\" data-end=\"1720\">Transform your space with the strength and look of polished concrete.</p><p data-start=\"1722\" data-end=\"1902\"><a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/schedule-a-visit/\"><strong data-start=\"1722\" data-end=\"1751\">Schedule an on-site visit</strong></a><br data-start=\"1751\" data-end=\"1754\" />Ready to plan your project. Call us or request an on-site visit. We\u2019ll walk the space, confirm scope, and deliver a clear plan, price, and timeline.</p><p data-start=\"1904\" data-end=\"1932\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\">Thank you,<br data-start=\"1914\" data-end=\"1917\" />Justin Campbell</p><ul><li><a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/staff-training/\">Staff Training</a></li><li><a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/7-essential-tips-for-impeccable-commercial-floor-care-services/\">7 Essential Tips for Impeccable Commercial Floor Care Services</a></li><li><a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/schedule-a-visit/\">Schedule Your Visit &amp; Quote</a></li><li><a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/faq/\">Frequently Asked Questions</a></li><li><a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/\">Home</a></li></ul><div style=\"background:#F3FCF4;border-left:4px solid #43A94B;padding:18px 22px;margin-top:24px;border-radius:6px\"><p style=\"margin:0 0 10px;font-size:13px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#0F1411\">Related Services</p><ul style=\"margin:0;padding-left:18px;line-height:1.9\"><li><a href=\"/long-term-recurring-commercial-floor-care-programs/\" style=\"color:#2F8137;font-weight:700\">Long-Term & Recurring Commercial Floor Care Services</a></li><li><a href=\"/customized-commercial-floor-care-solutions/\" style=\"color:#2F8137;font-weight:700\">Customized Commercial Floor Care Solutions</a></li><li><a href=\"/janitorial-housekeeping-facility-services/\" style=\"color:#2F8137;font-weight:700\">Janitorial & Housekeeping Facility Services</a></li><li><a href=\"/commercial-upholstery/\" style=\"color:#2F8137;font-weight:700\">Commercial Upholstery</a></li><li><a href=\"/commercial-tile-grout-cleaning-services/\" style=\"color:#2F8137;font-weight:700\">Commercial Tile & Grout Cleaning</a></li><li><a href=\"/commercial-carpet-cleaning-services/\" style=\"color:#2F8137;font-weight:700\">Commercial Carpet Cleaning Services</a></li></ul></div>",
                "align": "left",
